{"tid":1026708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連續第4年見紅！香港迪士尼去年錄5400萬虧損","createTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T10:36:46.000Z","uid":236891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c0981da4bae4b06d7346d8c23724b5ed2ec8da","tid":1026708,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/連續第4年見紅！香港迪士尼去年錄5400萬虧損-161961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%AC%AC4%E5%B9%B4%E8%A6%8B%E7%B4%85%EF%BC%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E9%8C%845400%E8%90%AC%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D-161961&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgDnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=b8a83324\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/連續第4年見紅！香港迪士尼去年錄5400萬虧損-161961</a><br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園公布2018財政年度業績，樂園全年入場人次達670萬，較2017年上升8%，本地客佔四成，內地客佔34%，其餘則為國際市場客。截止去年9月29日年結日，樂園全財政年度收入錄得60億元，上升18%；而未扣除利息、稅項、折舊及攤銷前盈利(EBITDA)則錄14億元，按年大增48%。<br />\n<br />\n樂園的收入及EBITDA均創下開園以來的紀錄，但樂園仍連續4年錄得虧損，2018財政年度的淨虧損為5,400萬元，但較2017年的3.45億元虧蝕大減84%。"},{"pid":"12f04ec1657b70970cbe8e8d1a6e3c75ebba9294","tid":1026708,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3786d0e640b1b48277f84e864ed4cee6c5aec5fd","tid":1026708,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24LsbR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24LsbR6.png&h=3de692a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjwSnYN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjwSnYN.png&h=39b27c96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb4c15804185e6207c5d58d43cb7e32c394a600c","tid":1026708,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:07:35.000Z","msg":"蝕少當贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\"